How are the stages of a pen test very similar to those of the Cyber Kill Chain?
      The stages of a pen test closely resemble the Cyber Kill Chain as both involve steps like reconnaissance, exploitation, and maintaining access to evaluate or compromise a network.


Your manager has asked you to explain the benefits of a pentest to the companyâ€™s leadership. How would you lead this conversation?
    I would start the conversation by highlighting that a penetration test proactively identifies and helps fix security vulnerabilities before they can be exploited by attackers
